            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Track Claude Design usage as a third weekly window (alongside All models and Sonnet)</li>
<li>Show Claude Design in macOS menu bar icon, popover, and Dashboard; iOS Dashboard; and Medium/Large widgets</li>
<li>Add <code>menuBarShowDesign</code> toggle in macOS Settings (Menu Bar Display)</li>
<li>Add <code>notifyDesign</code> threshold notifications in macOS Settings (Notifications)</li>
<li>Add Claude Design as a Live Activity metric on iOS</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
